description:
&lt;p&gt;Northamptonshire Healthcare NHS Foundation Trust is looking for an enthusiastic individual to assist with the development and maintenance of their accounting system and to manage the monitoring of capital expenditure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will assist with the day to day maintenance of the system and provide valuable input into the future developments of the ERP. The successful candidate will be forward thinking, innovative, able to work using their own initiative, able to adhere to deadlines and work within the strict audit requirements of a system environment. A strong knowledge of reporting procedures and system experience is desired.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameMark HitchingsJob titleSystems Development AccountantEmail addressmark.hitchings@nhft.nhs.ukTelephone number07526 918691&lt;/p&gt;
